node.text:
The BEST Beer Battered Onion Rings ever! The exterior is coated in an extra crispy, 'glass shattering' kind of coating once it's fried up and pairs perfectly with the soft and sweet onion on the inside! The best part is that our crispy, crunchy coating LASTS! So there's no need to worry about the first batch being soggy by the time you've fried up the last batch! 
- 
GET THE RECIPE: 
1️⃣ tap @spoonforkbacon
2️⃣👆Click link in profile
3️⃣👉Click on the picture to get straight to the recipe. 
Check out our "Recipe?" highlight for these instructions!
